ility for directing research through the <abbr title=\"Ministry of Defence\">MOD</abbr>’s core science and technology research portfolio. The <abbr title=\"Chief Scientific Adviser\">CSA</abbr> reports to the Permanent Secretary, and is a member of the Joint Requirements Oversight Committee and the Investment Approvals Committee.</p>\n\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-09-16T10:07:26Z","schema_name":"role","title":"MOD Chief Scientific Adviser","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2023-04-12T10:40:02Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Professor Dame Angela McLean - MOD Chief Scientific Adviser","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"f62c35f4-95df-4050-ba49-2ff5372927ab","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":2,"started_on":"2023-04-01T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"846dae81-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Government Chief Scientific Adviser (<abbr title=\"Government Chief Scientific Adviser\">GCSA</abbr>) is responsible for putting excellent science advice at the heart of decision making through:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>The provision of proactive and demand-led science advice to the <abbr title=\"Prime Minister\">PM</abbr> and Cabinet that is relevant, excellent, and delivered fit for purpose </li>\n  <li>Working across government to implement science advice mechanisms that are efficient, effective, speak truth to power and are embedded irreversibly in government systems.</li>\n</ul>\n\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-10-17T10:22:03Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Government Chief Scientific Adviser","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2023-04-03T08:32:06Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Professor Dame Angela McLean - Government Chief Scientific Advise